  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The European Hernia Society Guidelines of 2018 suggest that laparoscopic surgery should be&#xD;
      preferred over open surgery for bilateral inguinal hernia repair even though scientific&#xD;
      evidence are scarce. We will conduct a prospective, non randomise control trial, to&#xD;
      investigate the superiority of one technique over the other.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
